    "This command mentions the information of the added car, and the added car's information has been memorized by the project manager.",
    "This information is offered to the vehicle motion agent for determining the added police car's location.",
    "\"The view should be moved 5 meters ahead and 0.5 meters above.\"",
    "command is distributed to the view adjustment agent.",
    "The view adjustment agent returns the adjustment information of extrinsic as configuration, and calls the function to change the extrinsics to achieve view adjustment."
